e character with them at school or play dates. The encased LCD watch screen gives a digital time which is easy to read for kids who are just learning how to tell time.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">LEARN TO TELL TIME: Learning a new skill has never looked so good! This Toy Story 4 digital LED watch is a fantastic gift idea. Your child will develop the fundamental skills of telling time and time management while sporting their favorite polka dot mouse!</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">FUN DRESS UP ACCESSORY: The Toy Story 4 touchscreen watch is a fun accessory for young girls and boys to use when playing dress-up or during pretend play but is also a staple for everyday wear! This LED watch easily pairs with dress-up costumes and pretend play jewelry and accessories.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ONE SIZE FITS MOST: The kid’s LED touch screen kids smartwatch comes with a rubber band and buckle closure that fits most kids’ wrists. The comfortable adjustable strap features iconic images of Toy Story 4 for a fun and trendy look.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Face Cover Material: Plastic; Band Material: Rubber; Power Source: Battery; Wrist Circumference: Adjusts from 140mm to 240mm; Ages: 6+</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>Licensed Girls LED Display Digital Touch Screen Watch for Kids (18 Styles)</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">29.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>The Toy Story 4 Touchscreen LED watch is a great addition to any child’s wardrobe. Little Toy Story 4 fans will love having their favorite character with them at school or playdates. The black encased LCD watch screen gives a digital time that is easy to read for kids who are just learning how to tell time.\n\nLearning a new skill has never looked so good! This Toy Story 4 digital LED watch is a fantastic gift idea. Your child will develop the fundamental skills of telling time and time management while sporting their favorite character! The Toy Story 4 touchscreen watch is a fun accessory for young girls and boys to use when playing dress-up or during pretend play but is also a staple for everyday wear! This Toy Story 4 LED watch easily pairs with dress-up costumes and pretend play jewelry and accessories.\n\nThe kid’s LED touch screen kids smartwatch comes with a rubber band and buckle closure that fits most kids’ wrists. The comfortable adjustable strap features iconic images of Toy Story 4 for a fun and trendy look. This is a great gift idea this holiday season for kids and Disney fanatics!</p><p><strong>WARNING: Button/coin batteries can cause severe injuries or even death when swallowed. Keep batteries out of reach of children. If you suspect a child has swallowed or inserted a button/coin battery, seek medical attention immediately.</strong></p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\"